io.logspace.agent.api.event

Class AbstractEventBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.logspace.agent.api.event.AbstractEventBuilder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CxfEventBuilder, DefaultEventBuilder, JournalEventBuilder, JvmEventBuilder, OsEventBuilder, SolrEventBuilder

    public abstract class AbstractEventBuilder
extends Object
    Base class for Event Builders.
    Each instance is intended for creating a single Event.

    Subclasses should provide additional methods for setting specific EventProperties.
